<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fce7f3 0%, #e9d5ff 100%);
    }
    
    .email-container {
      background: white;
      margin: 20px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(139, 44, 127, 0.2);
    }
    
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #E91E8C 0%, #8B2C7F 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 40px 30px;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      border-bottom: 4px solid #4A1942;
    }
    
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0 0 10px 0;
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    
    .header p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-style: italic;
      opacity: 0.95;
      font-weight: 300;
    }
    
    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
      background: white;
    }
    
    .content h2 {
      color: #8B2C7F;
      font-size: 26px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 0 0 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .greeting {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #4A1942;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    
    .intro-text {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #374151;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }
    
    .job-title {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 800;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #E91E8C 0%, #8B2C7F 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 25px 0;
      padding: 15px;
      border-top: 3px solid #F8C8DC;
      border-bottom: 3px solid #F8C8DC;
    }
    
    .info-box {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fce7f3 0%, #e9d5ff 50%, #fce7f3 100%);
      padding: 25px;
      border-left: 6px solid #E91E8C;
      margin: 25px 0;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(233, 30, 140, 0.15);
    }
    
    .info-box strong {
      color: #8B2C7F;
      font-size: 18px;
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    
    .info-row {
      margin: 10px 0;
      padding: 8px 0;
      color: #4A1942;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    
    .info-row strong {
      display: inline;
      color: #8B2C7F;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 15px;
      margin-right: 8px;
    }
    
    .section-title {
      color: #8B2C7F;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 30px 0 15px 0;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #E91E8C;
    }
    
    .content ul {
      margin: 20px 0;
      padding-left: 25px;
    }
    
    .content li {
      margin: 12px 0;
      color: #374151;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    
    .cta-section {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 35px 0;
      padding: 25px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fce7f3 0%, white 100%);
      border-radius: 15px;
    }
    
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #E91E8C 0%, #d91479 100%);
      color: white !important;
      padding: 16px 40px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 30px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 16px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(233, 30, 140, 0.4);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      border: 3px solid transparent;
    }
    
    .button:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d91479 0%, #E91E8C 100%);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(233, 30, 140, 0.5);
    }
    
    .contact-info {
      background: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      margin: 25px 0;
      text-align: center;
      border: 2px solid #F8C8DC;
    }
    
    .contact-info p {
      margin: 10px 0;
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    
    .contact-info a {
      color: #E91E8C;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    
    .contact-info a:hover {
      color: #8B2C7F;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    
    .signature {
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 2px solid #F8C8DC;
      color: #374151;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    
    .signature strong {
      color: #8B2C7F;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    
    .footer {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8B2C7F 0%, #4A1942 100%);
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px;
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    
    .footer p {
      margin: 8px 0;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }
    
    .footer-logo {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
    
    .decorative-line {
      height: 4px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #E91E8C 0%, #8B2C7F 50%, #E91E8C 100%);
      margin: 30px 0;
      border-radius: 2px;
    }
    
    /* Responsive */
    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      .email-container {
        margin: 10px;
      }
      
      .header {
        padding: 30px 20px;
      }
      
      .header h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
      }
      
      .content {
        padding: 30px 20px;
      }
      
      .content h2 {
        font-size: 22px;
      }
      
      .job-title {
        font-size: 22px;
      }
      
      .button {
        padding: 14px 30px;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Yae Publishing House </h1>
      <p>Inazuma's Biggest Book Publishing Since 1984!</p>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Thank You for Your Application!</h2>
      
      <p class="greeting">Dear <%= @application.first_name %>,</p>
      
      <p class="intro-text">
        Thank you for applying to Yae Publishing House! We're excited to review your application and learn more about your passion for bringing stories to life.
      </p>
      
      <div class="job-title">
        <%= @job.title %>
      </div>
      
      <div class="info-box">
        <strong>Application Summary</strong>
        <div class="info-row">
          <strong>Position:</strong> <%= @job.title %>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <strong>Department:</strong> <%= @job.department.titleize %>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <strong>Location:</strong> <%= @job.location.titleize %>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <strong>Submitted:</strong> <%= @application.created_at.strftime('%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p') %>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="decorative-line"></div>
      
      <h3 class="section-title">What Happens Next?</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Review Process:</strong> Our recruitment team will carefully review your application and qualifications</li>
        <li><strong>Initial Screening:</strong> We'll reach out if your experience matches our requirements</li>
        <li><strong>Timeline:</strong> You can expect to hear from us within 2-3 weeks</li>
        <li><strong>Status Updates:</strong> We'll keep you informed throughout the process</li>
      </ul>
      
      <div class="cta-section">
        <p style="margin-bottom: 20px; color: #6b7280; font-size: 15px;">
          In the meantime, feel free to explore more opportunities with us:
        </p>
        <a href="<%= careers_url %>" class="button">
          View Open Positions
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="contact-info">
        <p><strong>Questions?</strong></p>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about your application, please don't hesitate to contact us at 
          <a href="mailto:<%= @job.contact_email || 'careers@yaepublishinghouse.com.in' %>">
            <%= @job.contact_email || 'careers@yaepublishinghouse.co.in' %>
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="signature">
        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p><strong>The Yae Publishing House Career Services</strong></p>
        <p style="color: #8B2C7F; font-style: italic; margin-top: 10px;">
          "Bringing stories to life, one page at a time"
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="footer">
      <div class="footer-logo">YAE PUBLISHING HOUSE</div>
      <p>Â© <%= Time.current.year %> Yae Publishing House. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>Inazuma's Premier Book Publisher Since 1984</p>
      <p style="font-size: 12px; opacity: 0.8; margin-top: 15px;">
        This is an automated message. Please do not reply directly to this email.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>